    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this one go. It\u2019s an absolute stunner and has been babied from day one. It\u2019s in truly flawless condition\u2014inside and out, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is your dream ride. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
